We are already using max-reading-parameters to limit number of metric parameters which is already being implemented.
This limit (max-number-metrics) is introduced to have a cap on number of metric properties (URI's) provided.
Example: 
{
ID: "MyMetric1",
MetricProperties: [
"/example1/test",
"/example2/test"
]
}
{
ID: "MyMetric2",
MetricProperties: [
"/example1/test",
"/example2/test"
]
}

So here we have 2 Metric Parameters (MyMetric1 and MyMetric2)
and 4 Metric parameters.

Am i missing something here ?
